channel.title: Webclient 99.9% Working, 1 problem, 1 question
channel.description:
Hey guys,
I recently followed I sora I's webclient TuT a few pages back, and I now have a working webclient. It loads on my computer very quickly, but when on the internet it stays on unpacking interfaces for 8 minutes+. Just wondering If thats to do with using a crap laptop with wireless modem in the middle of no where, or It is something with my client? I am stuck with a laptop for a long long time. If someone could test it for me? That'd be great, But I assume I wont be allowed to post my site on here.
QUESTION:
I am also looking at adding a console (No GUI, JGMS Client Base)
To my client to check to see if it has problems on the net, etc.
Kindest Regards,
Liam
